    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうしよう\n新曲、全然出来る気がしないよ～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wh-what should we do?\nWe’re not getting anywhere with the new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "どのアイデアもしっくり来ないわね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ none of the ideas feel right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 11.128140687942473
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "スランプ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Slump….",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.128140687942505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "完全に行き詰まってます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A total dead end…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.628140687942505,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 15.559410572052034
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "前に作詞した時も沢山悩んだけど\nここまで何も決まらないことはなかったわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We had lots of trouble writing the lyrics for the previous song‚\nbut we didn’t hit a roadblock as bad as this one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.79274390538534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 22.69274390538534
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだよ\nうーん、どうしてなのかなあ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s right…\nHmm. I wonder why that is.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.092743905385337,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 27.659410572052042
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "とにかく話し合いを続けましょう\n諦めずに続けていれば、きっと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let’s just keep brainstorming.\nIf we don’t give up and keep trying‚ I’m sure…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.559410572052006,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_knock-01.m4a",
          "delay": 3066.6666666666592,
          "startTime": 33.626077238718665
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 34.459410572052
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "stm",
      "speakerName": "橋本さとみ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Satomi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-satomi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-stm001.m4a",
      "text": "打ち合わせ中にすみません\n川咲さんは次の仕事があるので、そろそろ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry to interrupt your meeting‚\nbut Kawasaki-san needs to get ready for her next work.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.99274390538534,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 40.92607723871867
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "えっ、もうそんな時間？\nごめん、私もう行かないと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh?! It’s already time?\nSorry‚ I’ve got to go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.19274390538535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 45.65941057205201
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "仕事なんだから謝らなくていいわよ\n後は私達でやっておくから気にしないで",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s work. No need to apologize.\nWe’ll handle the song‚ so don’t worry.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.22607723871869,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "お仕事、頑張ってきてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good luck.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.19274390538536,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg1",
      "startTime": 55.1352609475454
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-skr004.m4a",
      "text": "うん、ありがとう\nそれじゃ、行ってくるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. Thank you.\nWell‚ see you all later.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.83526094754539,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "bg2",
      "startTime": 61.10192761421208
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
