    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nサニピのみんなの調子はどうですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nHow is everyone in Sunny Peace doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.301927614212055,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……曲作りは相変わらず難航してるよ\nなんとかしてやりたいんだが、どうしたものか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… they’re still struggling to write their new song.\nI’d love to help them‚ but I’m not sure how…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.93526094754539,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4799.999999999997,
          "startTime": 74.73526094754538
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこれを、後で読んで下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}-san!\nRead this when you have time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.40192761421204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "これは……レポート用紙の束？\nしかもかなり分厚いけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "A bundle of… reports?\nAnd a thick one‚ at that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.13526094754538,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "サニピが作詞・作曲で行き詰まっている件について\n私なりに要点と問題点をまとめてみました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I heard Sunny Peace was struggling with their songwriting‚\nI compiled a summary of the main points and issues.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.30192761421205,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "レポート用紙50枚にまとめておきましたので\nアドバイスする時の参考にして下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s a 50-page report‚\nso feel free to reference it when giving them advice.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.10311813354492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうか……沙季らしいな……\nでもどうしてこんなことを？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-really? Wow‚ that’s very like you‚ Saki.\nBut why did you do this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.83645146687822,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "それは……悩んでいるみんなの力に\n少しでもなれればと思って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… when I saw how troubled they looked‚\nI wanted to do what I could to help.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.36666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "月ストのみんなもサニピを心配しているんです\n私達はライバルでもあり……仲間ですから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone in Moon Tempest is worried about Sunny Peace.\nEven though we’re rivals… we’re also friends.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.86978480021165,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "……ありがとう、沙季\nレポートは参考にさせてもらうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ Saki.\nI’ll go over the report.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.50311813354487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "それと、もう一つ気になることがあるんですが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Also‚ there’s one other thing I’m worried about.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.00311813354487,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらのことなんですけど……\n最近、少し様子がおかしくありませんか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s Sakura…\nHave you noticed… she’s been acting a little strange lately?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.89502288500456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02/sud_vo_adv_main_02_03_02-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "さくらは辛くても弱音を吐かない所がありますから\n一人で思い詰めていないか心配で……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She’s the type of girl who never complains‚ even when she’s hurting.\nWe’re worried she’s keeping something to herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 134.26893454988803,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
